 men vi vurderer det \u00e5rlig. Likevel skal v\u00e5rt arbeid finansieres av gebyrene, avslutter Bente Haugr\u00f8nning."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "f9d4bbba137bc89574b7f43b8d18426d1e2a2c7a36fa201ed3c1ffb5c738e77b"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-07-21T10:01:39.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Irriterte naboer avsl\u00f8rer huseiere som starter bygging f\u00f8r de s\u00f8ker kommunen om lov. Bygningssjefen ansl\u00e5r at det p\u00e5g\u00e5r rundt 900 ulovlige byggetiltak i \u00e5ret."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1070002.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20bente_haugronning"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/ad0769c742644bed11c89ef2bcac40b35c498e25.jpg?5971d103"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "900 bygger ulovlig i Trondheim hvert \u00e5r -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "ad0769c742644bed11c89ef2bcac40b35c498e25"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["bygge", "byggetiltak", "saken", "s\u00f8ke", "irriterte naboer", "ulovlige byggetiltak", "ulovlige"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["brannvernprosjekt midtbyen", "m\u00f8llenberg", "bygningslovutvalget"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "bente haugr\u00f8nning"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1070002.